      "date": "2014-03-27 10:19:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/bf1f7a30-b595-11e3-b085-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity-sec.",
