    },
    {
      "id": "239837ecea270c8e9e2fe99a88157afb48ac9f8a",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 116,
        "name": "Brian J. Murrell",
        "email": "brian.murrell@intel.com",
        "username": "brian",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-04-15 19:38:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review+1\n\nJohn: Hi.  I had a chat with Eric and got a better handle on what the end goal was.  I had thought it was just disable-by-default, not complete removal.  In that light, this looks good.  I thought he was going to give you the nod to just go ahead, but in any case, here's my +1.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
